@startuml
autonumber
actor "Backoffice Operator" as BO
participant ":System" as System

activate BO
BO -> System : ask to view the Top 5 most utilized aircraft models (sortBy)
activate System

note right of System: The system aggregates flight hours\nand assignments per model across the fleet,\nsorts them, and limits the result to 5.

System --> BO : displays the Top 5 utilized models
deactivate System
deactivate BO
@enduml